# Dataset images are excluded from git (see .gitignore).
# Download the training data from the competition and place the images here:
#   trainval_data_final/training_data_final/
#
# Expected filename format: {index}_{real|fake}.png
# Example: 0003_fake.png, 0010_real.png
#
# The dataset can also be kept inside trainval_data_final/ directly
# and the config paths updated accordingly.
